title: @chickenwrap (ChOP'Gath Related)
body:
I was lookin through runes and stuff and I saw something.... seals have 0.5% max hp, there are also 1.5% max hp quints... and with the new Stoneborn Pact you can get an extra 5%.... for a grand total of 14% additional max hp... if you play jungle and get cinderhulk that synergizes with your runes...

you get my point.

the ChOP'Cheese era has begun
